data.description: Nestled on an acre in the heart of Castle Pines Village is this wonderful, secluded retreat waiting for its new owners. The home is full of mountain charm and loads of upgrades throughout. Greeted by a calming water feature, the home’s entrance is very welcoming. The two story foyer and living room immediately embrace visitors and draw them across to a wall of windows that frame the beauty of this serene location. A spacious gourmet kitchen will have you whipping up your culinary masterpieces while your friends and family gather around the approachable oversized island. Treat your loved ones right at the counter, in the kitchen nook or in the beautiful dining room. Unwind in the coveted main floor primary suite which includes an inviting fireplace, his and her closets and travertine heated floors in the bathroom suite. Upstairs includes a loft area with built in cabinets and desks as well as an office with its own private balcony. The remaining 4 bedrooms are generously sized and include en-suite bathrooms. A well organized retreat in the walk-out basement includes a game room, movie theater, workout room, steam shower, and a countertop bar with room for all. Get your game on outside on the sport court or 5 hole putting green. Relish the great Colorado outdoors from numerous decks, in the in-ground hot tub or in your private oasis around the firepit. This home was meticulously thought out and should not be missed!
